This is an implementation of a collection of shaders from ShaderToy.com
employed as visualization addon of XBMC/Kodi.


Requirements:
 - OpenGLES
 - Kodi 14 or higher


Build prerequisities:
 - sudo apt-get install kodi-addon-dev  (if not available in your repository, then add developer repository of kodi)


Tested on:
 - NVIDIA Jetson TK1 
 - Odroid XU4

 
